          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Course Rating represents the expected score of a scratch golfer (a golfer with a 0.0 handicap) under normal playing conditions. For a standard par 72 golf course, the Course Rating typically ranges between 68.0 and 74.0, depending on the length and obstacles of the course."
        }
      }
    ]
